---
name: CRM Architecture
description: CRM is premium-only hub with industry-specific embedded tools (AI Calendar, AI Pricing, etc.)
type: feature
---
- CRM (/crm) is ONLY for Premium subscribers and trial users
- Basic & Standard users see "Upgrade to Premium" gate
- Each industry gets different tools inside CRM based on crmTools config in crmConfig.ts
- Dashboard (/dashboard) remains accessible to ALL plans for basic scheduling
- Industries that need AI Pricing: hospitality, airlines, car_rental, events_entertainment, railways
- Industries WITHOUT AI Pricing: healthcare, education, logistics
- All industries get some form of scheduling (AI Calendar or AI Scheduling)
- industryFeatures.ts PRICING_INDUSTRIES set controls which industries get autoPricing/demandForecast
